commands.ew.unknown: &7Comando de eggwars desconocido. Escribe "/ew help" para la ayuda.
commands.ew.help:
&6&m----------&r&6[&aEggWars&6]&m----------
&aCommands:
&9 /ew join <arena name> &2- &7Joins an arena.
&9 /ew lang <locale> &2- &7Changes to the specified language.
&9 /ew lobby &2- &7Teleports you to the lobby.
&9 /ew randomJoin &2- &7Joins an available random arena.
&9 /ew forceStart <arena name> &2- &7Force an arena to start.
&9 /ew reload <all:config:languages:kits:generators:trades> &2- &7Reloads the specified configuration.
commands.setup.unknown: &7Comando de preparación desconocido. Escribe "/ews help" para la ayuda.
commands.setup.help:
&6&m----------&r&6[&aEggWars&6]&m----------
&aSetup commands:
&9 /ews help &2- &7Shows this list.
&9 /ews tpArena <arena name> &2- &7Teleports you to an arena.
&9 /ews setMainLobby &2- &7Sets the main lobby.
&9 /ews createArena <name> &2- &7Creates an arena.
&9 /ews removeArena <arena name> &2- &7Removes an arena.
&9 /ews cloneArena <existing arena> <new arena> &2- &7Clones an arena.
&9 /ews toggleEditMode <arena name> &2- &7Toggles an arena edit mode.
&9 /ews setWaitingLobby &2- &7Sets arena's waiting lobby.
&9 /ews setCenter &2- &7Sets arena center.
&9 /ews addTeam <team color> &2- &7Adds a team.
&9 /ews removeTeam <team color> &2- &7Removes the specified team.
&9 /ews moveTeam <old team color> <new team color> &2- &7Moves the specified team to another color.
&9 /ews setTeamEgg <team color> &2- &7Sets team's egg.
&9 /ews setTeamRespawn <team color> &2- &7Sets a team's respawn.
&9 /ews setTeamVillager <team color> &2- &7Sets team's villager location.
&9 /ews addTeamCage <team color> &2- &7Adds a cage for the team.
&9 /ews removeTeamCage <team color> &2- &7Removes the last cage of the team.
&9 /ews setBounds <xStart> <yStart> <zStart> <xEnd> <yEnd> <zEnd> &2- &7Sets the area of the arena where players can place blocks.
&9 /ews setStartCountdown <seconds> &2- &7Sets the arena lobby wait count down.
&9 /ews setFullCountdown <seconds> &2- &7Sets the new count down at lobby when the arena becomes full. Set it to -1 to disable this.
&9 /ews setReleaseCountdown <seconds> &2- &7Sets the count down time when waiting on cages.
&9 /ews setMaxPlayersPerTeam <number> &2- &7Sets max players per team number.
&9 /ews setMinPlayers <number> &2- &7Sets minimum number of players to start.
&9 /ews teamList &2- &7See every team of the arena. (Click to teleport).
